    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※若无法启动游戏，因此处无法粘贴度盘外链，请前往Q群获取缺少的系统组件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解压所得文件后，将所得三个dll文件拷贝粘贴至C:WindowsSysWOW64下即可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※或访问steam公告内的地址获取。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★★</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244080/extras/2d23578478f26b644f33a4beb9f0462f.webp?t=1770343968\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >澪是位探索地下城，渴望一攫千金的冒险家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一次探险途中不慎掉入一处陷阱之中，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >却因祸得福获得了一把名为“阿佛洛狄忒”的圣剑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而这把圣剑却有着提升所有者魅力，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进而魅惑魔物的可怕能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >澪在纠结是否丢掉圣剑的同时，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >继续踏上了探索地下城的旅途……。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244080/extras/f9b084fef737ed9147e0e53ac18d176b.webp?t=1770343968\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏为攻略地下城的ARPG。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家需要解谜的同时，与怪物战斗，继而在地下城中前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244080/extras/930eb57c84213306e6d1f045f093d9b7.webp?t=1770343968\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像素CG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解谜要素</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可选难易度</p></li></ul>",
